Features:
  Calendar
  Add events to calendar based on time or just day you would like todo them
  Shuffle event order on different days by dragging events
  Have events that are not day specific
  Have a schedule viewer to see todos for today / anything marked as "needs doing" / missed todos
  In this daily tasks view also include things that you would LIKE todo each day, if possible
  Dismiss functionality, especially if implementing push notifications
  Push notifications for todos
